data.description: Timber Trails Townhome featuring 2 bedrooms, a spacious loft, 2.5 baths and 2nd floor laundry!  The 2-story entryway leads you to an open floor plan with plenty of living space, a beautiful eat-in kitchen and a ground level exterior space with a patio. Other features include: 2-story living room, cathedral ceilings in the master bedroom,  newer flooring throughout (carpet + waterproof COREtec vinyl plank); smart thermostat; Black SS kitchen appliances 2020.   Fantastic location near shopping & dining plus easy access to I-90 & the Metra station.  This neighborhood offers bike/walking paths, playgrounds, and ponds!  Don't miss this lovingly cared for home!
